"title": "5765: attitudes, to other people",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5765: attitudes, to other people",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture illustrates a range of attitudes towards other people, some of which are commended, while others are condemned.</p>\n<h2>Love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34-John13:35\">JHN 13:34–13:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:39\">MAT 22:39</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:31\">MRK 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27\">LUK 10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:1-1Cor13:13\">1CO 13:1–13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:2\">EPH 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:9\">1TH 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:11\">1JN 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7\">1JN 4:7</a></p>\n<h2>Forgiveness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:13\">COL 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:14\">MAT 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:25\">MRK 11:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:37\">LUK 6:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:3\">LUK 17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:32\">EPH 4:32</a></p>\n<h2>Helpfulness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:36\">ACT 9:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:49\">EZK 16:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:44\">MAT 25:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:35\">ACT 20:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:28\">1CO 12:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:2\">2CO 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:9-1Tim5:10\">1TI 5:9–5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:10\">HEB 6:10</a></p>\n<h2>Hospitality</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:13\">ROM 12:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:1-Gen18:8\">GEN 18:1–18:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:38\">LUK 10:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:2\">HEB 13:2</a></p>\n<h2>Generosity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:2\">2CO 8:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:21\">PSA 37:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:26\">PSA 37:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:8\">MAT 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:2\">ACT 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:6-2Cor9:7\">2CO 9:6–9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:18\">1TI 6:18</a></p>\n<h2>Kindness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:32\">EPH 4:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:31\">PRO 14:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:4\">1CO 13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:24\">2TI 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:4-Titus2:5\">TIT 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h2>Humility</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:5\">1PE 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:34\">PRO 3:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:26-Matt20:28\">MAT 20:26–20:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:43-Mark10:45\">MRK 10:43–10:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:3-Phil2:8\">PHP 2:3–2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:1-Titus3:2\">TIT 3:1–3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:13\">JAS 3:13</a></p>\n<h2>Patience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:14\">1TH 5:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:32\">PRO 16:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:4\">1CO 13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22\">GAL 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:2\">EPH 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:11\">COL 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:7-Jas5:11\">JAS 5:7–5:11</a></p>\n<h2>Submission</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:21\">EPH 5:21</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1\">ROM 13:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:5\">ROM 13:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:13\">1PE 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:22-Eph5:24\">EPH 5:22–5:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:18\">COL 3:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:11\">1TI 2:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:1\">1PE 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:5-1Pet3:6\">1PE 3:5–3:6</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:17\">JAS 3:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:18\">1PE 2:18</a> <em>submission of slaves to masters</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:5\">1PE 5:5</a></p>\n<h2>Gentleness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:5\">PHP 4:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:23\">GAL 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:2\">EPH 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a></p>\n<h2>Unselfishness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:4\">PHP 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:1\">PRO 18:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:19-Gal5:20\">GAL 5:19–5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:17\">PHP 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:14\">JAS 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:16\">JAS 3:16</a></p>\n<h2>Pride</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:16\">ROM 12:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:13\">PRO 8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7\">2CO 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:26\">GAL 5:26</a></p>\n<h2>Jealousy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:4\">PRO 27:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:1\">GEN 30:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:11\">GEN 37:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:17\">ACT 5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:9\">ACT 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:3\">1CO 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:20\">2CO 12:20</a></p>\n<h2>Judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:37\">LUK 6:37</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:1\">MAT 7:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:3-John8:7\">JHN 8:3–8:7</a></p>\n<h2>Anger</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:31\">EPH 4:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:3-Gen4:5\">GEN 4:3–4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:11\">2KI 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:5\">MRK 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:26\">EPH 4:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:8\">1TI 2:8</a></p>\n<h2>Hatred</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:15\">1JN 3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:9\">1JN 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:11\">1JN 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:20\">1JN 4:20</a></p>\n<h2>Partiality</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:3\">GEN 37:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:28\">GEN 25:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:3\">EXO 23:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:15\">LEV 19:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:21\">1TI 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1-Jas2:4\">JAS 2:1–2:4</a></p>",
